title: Wrap Battle
overview: A holiday gift-wrapping competition series, Wrap Battle follows nine contestants as they battle to become the ultimate wrapper and take home the coveted grand prize, valued at $50,000.Nine contestants will be challenged to create eye-popping gift-wrapping masterpieces and inspire viewers to push their own holiday gift-giving to a whole new level. Each episode will pit the country's most inventive and artistic gift-wrappers against one another as they battle it out holiday-style in challenges ranging from creating the most over-the-top gift basket to wrapping some of the most outrageous objects.
